{"tid":1494094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"裝夠了人面識別鏡頭，就係運動失敗之時","createTime":"2019-08-21T13:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T04:16:04.000Z","uid":280192,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"346ad1257024b69cbe5aae7fecc48468755f8a4c","tid":1494094,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"政府只要拖到有一日，到處係鏡頭，就可以正式企硬然後大清算。勇武到時無辦法再做任何衝擊，一衝就會比人追查到逮捕。咁到時和理非亦都無用，因為政府係怕大量和理非支持勇武。<br />\n<br />\n我係大陸見過，就算在山上點支煙，不久都會有班公安衝上山警告，仲可以知道你叫乜名等資料。所以大陸已無人敢衝。<br />\n<br />\n唔想呢個運動輸，就要以保護私隱為理由禁止隨意裝鏡頭(雖然應該無用，但都要做)，甚至要以6.12阻擋立法會開會嘅決心，阻擋一切安裝。<br />\n<br />\n大家切記，比人裝曬cam就同送左中無分別，整場運動輸掉變新疆。"},{"pid":"80453c5d6385a85fd12aaeca73beeadcaa0abc13","tid":1494094,"uid":200666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:52:03.000Z","msg":"可唔可以每次夢遊都破壞曬嗰邊啲人面識別鏡頭"},{"pid":"928eca86938375f786af94c8c74619820af9174f","tid":1494094,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:52:25.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"ff5c8e9411b29df05cfbdb7cc08a7014fe77c46b","tid":1494094,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"拆一裝百，搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d941bf0425a71d864dd7a079a2fc50bc7cedda","tid":1494094,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:53:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dHmAvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dHmAvS</a>"},{"pid":"8dfb7d10dda64493d00b8bd709b52c26a39cc82e","tid":1494094,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:53:54.000Z","msg":"元朗 @2148 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/mid/2954daee821566390909746\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2Fmid%2F2954daee821566390909746&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn013VpWtqcNNCz